snippet.title: Sky Shark (NES) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A playthrough of Taito's 1989 vertically-scrolling shoot 'em up for the NES, Sky Shark. 

The game has no formal ending, in case you are wondering if I had somehow forgotten to include it. It merely loops again once you reach the end of the fifth stage. At the end of the video I go back to the title screen so you could hear the full theme music - Tim Follin is awesome. 

I've already done a full write-up on Sky Shark on my website, so if you are interested in learning more, please check it out! http://www.nintendocomplete.com/sky-shark

______________________
No cheats were used during the recording of this video.
